originalText.text: Tara was amazing from our first conversation. She took the time to get to know me and what I wanted my birth to be like, going so far as to research Drs, birthing centers and parental rights so I was always informed about my options. She was present throughout my entire pregnancy and continuously checked in on me. When plans changed and I ended up having to have a C-Section, Tara  joined me I'm the operating room and stayed with me until visiting hours were over. She came back the next day, fed me and kept me from going insane while I waited for the opportunity to see my baby. Afterwards, she has continued to check up on us and congratulate us on each milestone my beautiful girl has reached. I plan on using Tara again with any future pregnancies I may have. I highly recommend her!
